    • Method Detail

      • setPassword

        public static void setPassword(org.apache.xmlbeans.XmlObject xobj,
                               java.lang.String password,
                               HashAlgorithm hashAlgo,
                               java.lang.String prefix)
        Sets the XORed or hashed password(设置XOR或哈希密码)
        Parameters:
        xobj - the xmlbeans object which contains the password attributes(xobj -包含密码属性的xmlbeans对象)
        password - the password, if null, the password attributes will be removed(密码-密码，如果为空，则将删除密码属性)
        hashAlgo - the hash algorithm, if null the password will be XORed(hashAlgo -哈希算法，如果为空，密码将被异或)
        prefix - the prefix of the password attributes, may be null(prefuse-密码属性的prefuse，可以为空)

      • validatePassword

        public static boolean validatePassword(org.apache.xmlbeans.XmlObject xobj,
                                       java.lang.String password,
                                       java.lang.String prefix)
        Validates the password, i.e. calculates the hash of the given password and compares it against the stored hash(验证密码，即计算给定密码的哈希值并将其与存储的哈希值进行比较)
        Parameters:
        xobj - the xmlbeans object which contains the password attributes(xobj -包含密码属性的xmlbeans对象)
        password - the password, if null the method will always return false, even if there's no password set(password -密码，如果为null，方法将始终返回false，即使没有设置密码)
        prefix - the prefix of the password attributes, may be null(prefuse-密码属性的prefuse，可以为空)
        Returns:
        true, if the hashes match(如果哈希值匹配，则为真)
